  "keyFeatures": [
    "Dual microservice architecture (Python Flask + Node.js Express)",
    "JWT-based authentication with bcrypt password hashing",
    "RESTful APIs for e-commerce operations (products, orders, payments)",
    "SQLAlchemy and Sequelize ORM integration",
    "Docker Compose orchestration with PostgreSQL and Redis",
    "Comprehensive test suites with pytest and Jest",
    "Structured incident tracking system",
    "User management with profile operations"
